how much time you have left?

32:56.608 --> 32:58.442
No, and now's not the time.

32:58.444 --> 33:01.778
When you get to oncentric,
you can look for otto, too.

33:01.780 --> 33:03.947
We're going for gracie.

33:03.949 --> 33:06.583
Anything of hers --
a shirt, a scarf.

33:06.585 --> 33:08.785
