when someone is lost.

33:08.787 --> 33:11.121
Where is she, duval?
Isn't she with that boy?

33:11.123 --> 33:14.191
Please, helen, just do this.
Bring it to us.

33:14.193 --> 33:16.326
[ phone beeps ]

33:16.328 --> 33:18.528
[ whirring ]

33:22.800 --> 33:24.234
Let's go.

33:59.871 --> 34:02.939
[ siren winds down
and police radio chatter ]

