Get the warrant?
Yeah.

34:13.419 --> 34:15.252
Are you gonna
let me see it?

34:15.254 --> 34:18.188
It'd be better
if you didn't.

34:18.190 --> 34:21.591
Be better for you if you could
say I told you it was good.

34:21.593 --> 34:24.094
