for the search of this building.

34:59.364 --> 35:01.131
Everyone needs to step away
from their work.

35:01.133 --> 35:03.200
All the doors
shall be unlocked.

35:03.202 --> 35:04.668
Graff's office is
which way?

35:09.440 --> 35:11.108
We'll take graff.

35:11.110 --> 35:12.809
You take the team
through the building.

35:17.248 --> 35:19.816
Okay, everybody,
work the grid.

35:27.658 --> 35:30.560
That's as far as you go.
Like hell it --
[ grunts ]

35:32.597 --> 35:35.665
