that was a bit extreme,
but I'll go with it for now.

35:35.667 --> 35:37.667
How can I help the fbi?
Open this door!

35:37.669 --> 35:39.603
And don't even bother
with that piece of crap warrant.

35:39.605 --> 35:40.937
I called about it
when I saw you pull in.

35:40.939 --> 35:43.240
Open up!
Where's my daughter?

35:44.909 --> 35:46.109
I-I don't know
your daughter.

35:46.111 --> 35:47.177
Wrong answer.

35:51.482 --> 35:53.650
That help you
remember, huh?

35:57.955 --> 36:00.357
Her name is
gracie pritchard.

36:00.359 --> 36:02.025
She has
the genetic precursor.

36:02.027 --> 36:03.827
The genetic what now?

36:03.829 --> 36:06.696
You will tell me
where she is.

36:06.698 --> 36:08.131
Gracie who?

36:08.133 --> 36:10.100
I honestly don't know
who you're talking about.

36:10.102 --> 36:11.701
Oh, you honestly?
Honestly, huh?

36:12.770 --> 36:14.771
Security guard:
Open up!
Duval, throttle back.

36:14.773 --> 36:16.840
We need him talking.

36:16.842 --> 36:18.842
[ strained ] you're making
a big mistake here.

36:22.346 --> 36:23.547
Where is she?!

36:23.549 --> 36:24.981
Get off!
Let me go!

36:24.983 --> 36:26.483
Where is she?!

36:26.485 --> 36:27.384
Let me go!

36:27.386 --> 36:29.286
Where is she?!
Let me go!

36:29.288 --> 36:30.387
Calm down!
Calm down.

36:30.389 --> 36:31.888
That's enough!

36:31.890 --> 36:34.658
That agent attacked me!

36:34.660 --> 36:36.960
You've got
a big problem here.

36:36.962 --> 36:39.796
Duval: He took my daughter.
He took her.

36:39.798 --> 36:42.632
I know what it looks like,
but there was no other way.

36:42.634 --> 36:43.800
He took my daughter.

36:43.802 --> 36:45.635
Let me tell you
what this looks like.

36:45.637 --> 36:47.871
It looks like
you were assaulting mr. Graff

36:47.873 --> 36:49.973
And your c.I. Was attempting
to restrain you.

36:49.975 --> 36:53.243
It <i>looks</i> like you knowingly
led a team of agents in here

36:53.245 --> 36:54.477
With a fraudulent warrant.

36:54.479 --> 36:55.745
You need
to let me explain.

36:55.747 --> 36:59.349
No, you need to meet me
downstairs, both of you.

36:59.351 --> 37:01.084
These agents will make sure

37:01.086 --> 37:03.153
You don't get into
anymore trouble.

37:11.929 --> 37:13.930
Mr. Graff,
I want to assure you

37:13.932 --> 37:16.066
None of this was approved
by the bureau.

37:16.068 --> 37:19.669
Just talk to my lawyers.
Okay, honey?

37:53.271 --> 37:54.971
Stand down.

37:54.973 --> 37:56.940
Did your c.I. Know
that warrant was fake?

37:56.942 --> 37:58.808
No, ma'am, he didn't.

37:58.810 --> 38:00.910
None of the agents did,
just me.

38:00.912 --> 38:02.912
Okay, I want you
out of here.

38:02.914 --> 38:04.447
Gracie's probably
just with some friends.

38:04.449 --> 38:06.182
I'll find her.
I promise.

38:08.219 --> 38:11.321
Graff let us search it,
the offices and the labs.

38:11.323 --> 38:13.423
We used the dog
with gracie's scent.

38:13.425 --> 38:15.825
She's not here.
He doesn't have her.

38:15.827 --> 38:17.227
Gracie ran away.

38:17.229 --> 38:18.495
[ voice breaking ]
they made it look like that.

38:18.497 --> 38:19.896
Agent pritchard --

38:19.898 --> 38:21.831
He made it look like gloria's
death was a hit-and-run,

38:21.833 --> 38:24.567
Made it look like that john doe
did the killings.

38:24.569 --> 38:26.269
Why?
Why would he do that?

38:26.271 --> 38:29.172
[ sighs ]

38:29.174 --> 38:32.275
Gracie has a precursor
in her dna.

38:32.277 --> 38:34.978
She can be regenerated,
brought back from the dead.

38:34.980 --> 38:37.747
I know it sounds crazy.

38:37.749 --> 38:40.684
My father has it, too.

38:40.686 --> 38:42.285
Your father has it?

38:42.287 --> 38:45.288
Yeah. Him.
That's my father.

38:45.290 --> 38:47.657
Test his dna.
He has it, too.

38:50.428 --> 38:52.662
That's why
connor took her.

38:55.599 --> 38:58.301
Agent pritchard,
I'm relieving you of duty

38:58.303 --> 38:59.769
Effective immediately.

38:59.771 --> 39:02.605
You will surrender your gun
and your badge to me.

39:02.607 --> 39:06.242
I'm remanding you
to a 72-hour psych hold.

39:08.946 --> 39:11.381
Charges will be
brought against you for assault

39:11.383 --> 39:13.383
And falsifying
a court order.

39:13.385 --> 39:16.419
You will allow these agents
to place you in restraints.

39:28.699 --> 39:30.166
[ handcuffs click ]

39:30.168 --> 39:34.003
You need to go back in there.
He has my daughter.

39:34.005 --> 39:36.039
Please.

39:38.175 --> 39:48.084
Oh, man.
Just like his dad.

39:48.086 --> 39:51.154
