Just rugby.
Is everything ready here?

40:26.625 --> 40:28.892
This is what mary said
not to do.

40:28.894 --> 40:30.794
Mary said not to dream.

40:30.796 --> 40:33.930
I mean, she got hers.
Why can't you have yours?

40:36.434 --> 40:37.934
Arthur.

40:37.936 --> 40:39.436
<i>Yes, otto.</i>

40:39.438 --> 40:42.439
Begin taking notes.
[ beep ]

40:42.441 --> 40:45.275
Procedure 001.

40:45.277 --> 40:48.878
First attempt at stripping
the precursor from the dna of...

40:48.880 --> 40:53.483
<i>Her name is gracie pritchard.</i>

40:53.485 --> 40:55.952
I know her name.

40:55.954 --> 40:58.021
Call her
test subject zero.

41:00.224 --> 41:04.461
The process will induce
a seizure...

41:04.463 --> 41:07.263
And great deal of pain.

41:07.265 --> 41:09.933
The subject has been given a
sufficient amount of anesthesia,

41:09.935 --> 41:11.701
Though, upon waking...

41:14.839 --> 41:17.640
...The aftereffects
may be permanent.

41:20.511 --> 41:22.779
Initiate phase one,
arthur.

41:22.781 --> 41:25.615
<i>Phase one initiated.</i>

41:25.617 --> 41:29.352
[ moaning ]
[ electricity crackling ]

41:29.354 --> 41:31.754
[ indistinct conversations ]

41:52.109 --> 41:54.611
I think
you're looking for me.

41:54.613 --> 41:57.981
Call security.
No. Please.

41:57.983 --> 42:00.183
Let me --
let you what, alexa?

42:00.185 --> 42:03.286
Otto is gone,
lookinglass is gone,

42:03.288 --> 42:05.788
And soon,
pritchard will be, too.

42:05.790 --> 42:08.358
What are you here
to take from me now?

42:08.360 --> 42:10.293
[ crying ] nothing.

42:10.295 --> 42:13.196
I just came to help you.

42:13.198 --> 42:14.697
I know where gracie is,

42:14.699 --> 42:18.401
And I know where
connor graff has her.

42:18.403 --> 42:22.138
Where?

42:22.140 --> 42:25.842
In the place
where connor finished me...

42:25.844 --> 42:29.846
After your brother
threw me away.

